  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Vision Development Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong><br /></p><p>You are required to develop and maintain new and existing vision applications. Key functions include requirement analysis, sample evaluation, hardware testing, image analysis, software design, coding, testing, integration, documentation and customer training.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Degree / Diploma in EEE/Software Engineering/Computer Science.</li><li>3 years working experience in vision application development with hardware selection and software implementation</li><li>Experience in develop and implement a vision inspection system with AI deep learning capabilities with software engine/tools like *VPDL, *VisionTrain etc.. will be added advantage</li><li>Experience in software programming using C# with Microsoft Visual Studio.</li><li>Experience in PC based software design and implementation in auto machine/equipment development will be an added advantage.</li><li>Experience in Microsoft C# will be an added advantage.</li><li>Willing to learn and adapt to new technology quickly.</li><li>Ability to work independently.</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Able to travel overseas.</li></ul><p><br />\n\n</p>",
